The "Windows 7" type skin and icon used in many of the screenshots of Circle Dock 0.9.2 come from Stefan Vd: http://www.stefanvd.net/google_gadget/windows_dock.htm (GNU General Public License).
The Circle Dock program icon was taken from the Oxygen icon set by roundbone (http://roundbone.deviantart.com/art/Oxygen-58157583).
Some icons and skins included with the program were taken from Rocket Dock (http://rocketdock.com/download) under a Creative Commons License (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0>) .
Some icons and code were taken from Orbit Dock by Lucas Menge (Open Source - No specific license. Must keep derivative code open source.): http://www.ecocardio.com.br/orbit/
Some icons were taken from http://deleket.deviantart.com under a Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial-No Derivative Works 3.0 License.
